These 17 Things Don't Matter đ đťđ đźđ đ˝đ đż when You're Madly đ in Love đ ... 
When you're in love , nothing else matters. 
You won't care what your boyfriend looks like or where he's from, as long as you two make each other happy. 
After all, happiness is the most important thing in life. 
That's why these #things don't really matter when you're madly in love: 1. How Much Money He Makes 
As long as you two can survive on your combined paychecks, why would it matter how much money he makes? 
You don't need to be rich in order to feel blessed.
